SESSION.DESCRIPTION: Session to load cutting standard cost in STG_STANDARD_COST table
SESSION.NAME: s_m_STG_STD_COST_UOM

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET TGT_VAL=( SELECT count(*) FROM STG_STANDARD_COST WHERE PRS_TSP= (SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_STD_COST_UOM' AND MAP_RUN_DT > (TRUNC(SYSDATE) - 1) )) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_STD_COST_UOM' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_STD_COST_UOM' AND MAP_RUN_DT > (TRUNC(SYSDATE) - 1) ) ;
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET STATUS_YN = (CASE WHEN SRC_VAL = TGT_VAL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_STD_COST_UOM' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_STD_COST_UOM')
